longBusinessSummary: Hifab Group AB (publ) provides project management and consulting services in Sweden, rest of Europe, Asia, and Africa. It offers advisory services in the real estate and civil engineering industry. Hifab Group AB (publ) was founded in 1947 and is headquartered in Stockholm, Sweden.
